Call Lightning

A druid of sufficient power may channel the power of
the storm, drawing forth lightning out of even the
clearest skies.  Aside from the damage it causes,
this spell has a high chance of stunning its target
for a short time.  It also causes greater damage
against flying targets, since it is an air-element
spell.

Command: lightning <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 5 * guild level SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: damage (high)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 20
